title: Jeffrey Epstein Victim Says She May Have Made a Mistake in Accusing Dershowitz
description: Virginia Giuffre, who was trafficked as a girl by Jeffrey E. Epstein, had accused Alan Dershowitz of abusing her. Now she says she is no longer certain.
dc:creator: Katherine Rosman and Jonah E. Bromwich
media:credit: Alyssa Schukar for The New York Times
media:description: Alan Dershowitz said Virginia Giuffre was brave to acknowledge that she might have been mistaken.
